1. https://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/guides/bug_report_templates/active_record_gem.rb
2. .rspec reuire --require rails_helper because in your case you add spec_helper in rails helper not a rails helper in spec helper.
3. Use include Rails.application.routes.url_helpers to get route path and url in anywhere you can also use this in console.
4. Rails s run automatically with capybara testing if it include rails helper otherwise you have to run it yourself.
5. Spec testing file name should be end with spec so that when you run bundle exec rspec it run all specs automatically.
6. Debugger in spec stop at console at your debugger position.


